'''飓风格特'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Gert}}）是1993年9月一场在墨西哥和整个中美洲引发严重洪灾的大规模[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是1993年大西洋飓风季第7场获得命名的风暴和第3场飓风，源于9月14日西南[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]上空一股[[东风波|东风波]]{{#tag:ref|[[东风波|东风波]]指的是沿[[信风|信风]]移动的[[低压槽|低压槽]]<ref name="glos">{{cite report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-03-25 | accessdate = 2014-06-15 | title = Glossary of NHC Terms | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601020814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml}}</ref>。|group="注"}}发展而成的热带低气压。次日，气旋短暂达到热带风暴强度并从[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]登岸，经过[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]后于9月17日在[[洪都拉斯湾|洪都拉斯湾]]再次达到热带风暴标准，但次日进入[[伯利兹|伯利兹]]上空后就减弱成热带低气压。穿过[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]后，格特接触到[[坎佩切湾|坎佩切湾]]的温暖水域，令其得以在9月20日强化成[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|二级飓风]]。飓风以每小时165公里的[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]从[[韦拉克鲁斯州|韦拉克鲁斯州]]的[[图斯潘_(韦拉克鲁斯州)|图斯潘]]附近登陆墨西哥的墨西哥湾沿岸地区。崎岖的地形很快打断了气旋的结构，格特于9月21日从[[纳亚里特州|纳亚里特州]]进入[[太平洋|太平洋]]时已降级成热带低气压。系统在太平洋中有过短暂的发展，一度拥有少许强烈[[雷暴|雷暴]]，最终于5天后在开放水域上空消散。

格特的大规模环流给整个中美洲带去了大范围且持久的暴雨，这些地区刚在一个月前受到[[1993年热带风暴布雷特|热带风暴布雷特]]的袭击，土壤含水量处于饱和状态，因此出现了大规模洪灾，给财物和农作物造成严重损失。虽然风暴的最强风力出现在登陆墨西哥时，但该国所受破坏仍以降水引发的洪水最为严重。多条主要河流溢出或决口，导致[[韦拉克鲁斯州|韦拉克鲁斯州]]和[[塔毛利帕斯州|塔毛利帕斯州]]大量区域被水淹没，成千上万的居民被迫撤离。降雨量最大的是深入内陆的[[圣路易斯波托西州|圣路易斯波托西州]]山区，局部降雨量高达798毫米。灾难发生后，多个国家交通和通讯受到严重扰乱，成千上万的居民流离失所，[[国际社会|国际社会]]纷纷主动提供援助。这场风暴共计夺走了至少90人的生命，还有至少43人失踪，经济损失达1.7亿美元（1993年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|170000000|1993}}}}美元）。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Gert-14 1993 track.png}}
1993年9月5日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]从[[达喀尔|达喀尔]]以南离开[[非洲|非洲]]海岸，以较快的速度向西穿越热带[[大西洋|大西洋]]。由于所在位置[[纬度|纬度]]相对较低，东风波与[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]发生相互作用，附近的[[对流|对流]]得以强化。系统在海平面位置发展出弱[[低气压|低气压中心]]，该中心于9月11日直接从[[特立尼达岛|特立尼达岛]]上空经过。系统中大部分天气活动随后沿[[南美洲|南美洲]]北部海岸移入内陆，除下的仍然保持热带系统特征，于9月13日进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]西南部上空<ref name="prelim01">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/prenhc/prelim01.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025070316/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/prenhc/prelim01.gif | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Gert: 14-21 September 1993 | series = Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | date = 1993-11-10 | first = Richard J. | last = Pasch | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | location = Miami, Florida | publisher = National Hurricane Center | page = 1 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | deadurl = no | format = GIF}}</ref>。由于外部[[对流层|对流层]]环境有利，系统开始表现出发展迹象，有深层对流组织成层次分明的弧形[[雨带|雨带]]。由于系统的组织结构有所强化，并且出现了表面环流，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]9月14日下午18点将其归类为[[热带气旋|热带低气压]]，气旋这时位于[[巴拿马|巴拿马]]北部海岸以北约165公里海域<ref name="prelim01" /><ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140718153135/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.001 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.001 | title = Tropical Depression Eight Discussion One | series = Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | date = 1993-09-14 | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | last = Pasch | first = Richard J. | location = Miami, Florida | publisher = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-07-18}}</ref>。

经[[气象卫星|卫星观测]]和该地区的[[无线电探空仪|无线电探空仪]]数据显示，低气压在形成阶段保留着大规模的环流<ref name="prelim01" />。其云层格局继续聚结，美国国家飓风中心于9月15日将其升级成热带风暴并以“格特”（{{lang|en|Gert}}）命名<ref>{{cite report | title = Tropical Storm Gert Discussion Three | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140718153839/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.003 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.003 | series = Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | date = 1993-09-15 | accessdate = 2014-07-18 | last = Pasch | first = Richard J. | location = Miami, Florida | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2014-07-18}}</ref>。向西北偏西方向行进一段时间后，风暴中心于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}当天下午18点以[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]65公里强度从[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]的[[布卢菲尔兹|布卢菲尔兹]]附近登岸<ref name="prelim01" /><ref name="besttrack">{{cite report | url = | location = Miami, Florida | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1993-11-10 | first = Richard J. | last = Pasch | accessdate = 2011-10-06 | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Gert: 14-21 September 1993 | series = Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | at = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/prenhc/prelim05.gif Table 1: Preliminary best track, Hurricane Gert, 14-21 September 1993]}}</ref>。由于与陆地间存在相互作用，风暴无法得到进一步发展，6小时后，格特就降级成热带低气压。虽然气旋中心在内陆上空逗留了近两天，但大部分环流还是保持在邻近的加勒海比和[[太平洋|太平洋]]水域上空。这使得系统可以在向西北方向前进、先后途经尼加拉瓜和[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]的过程中仍然保持着热带气旋的特征<ref name="prelim01" />，而没有像美国国家飓风中心多次预料的那样在陆地上空消散<ref>{{cite report | date = 1993-10-15 | last = Pasch | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140718162322/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.005 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.005 | title = Tropical Depression Gert Discussion Five | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Richard J. | location = Miami, Florida | series = Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | archivedate = 2014-07-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.009 | title = Tropical Depression Gert Discussion Nine | date = 1993-10-16 | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Richard J. | last = Pasch | location = Miami, Florida | series = Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140718162510/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.009 | archivedate = 2014-07-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。
[[File:14-E_1993.jpg|175px]]

9月17日，气旋进入[[洪都拉斯湾|洪都拉斯湾]]并很快增强成热带风暴。同日，风暴因受到东部[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]上空一片中到上层[[低压槽|低压槽]]的影响转向西北偏北。格特在水面上空持续的时间较短，次日就从[[伯利兹市|伯利兹市]]附近再次登岸，所以没有多少时间获得进一步强化。进入陆地上空后，系统开始受到西北方向一片[[高压脊|高压脊]]的影响而再度转朝西北偏西方向移动<ref name="prelim02">{{cite report | location = Miami, Florida | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Gert: 14-21 September 1993 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/prenhc/prelim02.gif | date = 1993-11-10 | first = Richard J. | last = Pasch | accessdate = 2011-10-03 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | series = Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | page = 2 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025070322/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/prenhc/prelim02.gif}}</ref>。风暴在穿越[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]期间组织性持续减弱<ref>{{cite report | archivedate = 2014-07-18 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.016 | title = Tropical Depression Gert Discussion Sixteen | date = 1993-10-18 | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Miles B. | last = Lawrence | location = Miami, Florida | series = Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140718172654/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.016 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，于9月18日晚以热带低气压强度从[[坎佩切州|坎佩切州]]的[[钱波通|钱波通]]（{{lang|es|Champotón}}）进入[[坎佩切湾|坎佩切湾]]<ref name="besttrack" /><ref name="prelim02" />。进入开放水域上空后，由于[[风切变|风切变]]很少，格特的深层对流得以巩固，到{{lang|en|UTC}}次日早上6点，气旋已再一次成为热带风暴<ref>{{cite report | location = Miami, Florida | series = Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.019 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140719023256/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.019 | title = Tropical Storm Gert Discussion Nineteen | date = 1993-09-19 | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | first = Max | last = Mayfield | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2014-07-19}}</ref>。9月20日，[[美国空军|美国空军]]一架[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]][[侦察机|侦察机]]的数据表明风暴已进一步达到风速每小时120公里强度，升级成了飓风。格特调头向西，并且前进速度因北面一个短波槽的影响略有放缓<ref>{{cite report | archivedate = 2014-07-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140719023701/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.023 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.023 | title = Hurricane Gert Discussion Twenty-Three | date = 1993-09-23 | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Max | last = Mayfield | location = Miami, Florida | series = Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives}}</ref><ref>{{cite report | title = Hurricane Gert Discussion Twenty-Four | first1 = Edward N. | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140719023827/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.024 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/tropdisc/nal0893.024 | last1 = Rappaport | first2 = Bill | last2 = Wright | date = 1993-09-19 | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | series = Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | archivedate = 2014-07-19 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，风暴也因此有了更多的时间在水上发展<ref name="prelim02" />。气旋最终达到了风力时速165公里，最低[[气压|气压]]970[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.64[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度，可以在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下达到二级飓风标准<ref name="prelim02" />。

{{lang|en|UTC}}9月20日晚21点左右，格特以最高强度从[[韦拉克鲁斯州|韦拉克鲁斯州]][[图斯潘_(韦拉克鲁斯州)|图斯潘]]以西不远处[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[墨西哥|墨西哥]]海岸。进入陆地上空后，飓风行进速度加快并在[[东马德雷山脉|东马德雷山脉]]上空迅速减弱，到9月21日时已退化成热带低气压。不过系统强度虽大幅减弱，但其大规模环流在穿越该国的过程中却几乎没有受到影响。低气压于当晚从[[纳亚里特州|纳亚里特州]]海岸进入太平洋，美国国家飓风中心因此将其重新归类为[[1993年太平洋飓风季|1993年太平洋飓风季]]的第十四{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压<ref name="besttrack" /><ref name="prelim02" />。残留的深层对流强度跌宕起伏，卫星观测数据表明低气压可能会在9月22日短暂增强成热带风暴。气旋之后两天继续向西北偏西方向飘移，对流消散后，下层气流令系统向西南转向。由于[[海面温度|海面温度]]低，系统无法得到再度发展，于9月26日在海上消散<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1993/td14e/prenhc/prelim01.gif | title = Preliminary Report Tropical Depression Fourteen-E: 21-26 September 1993 | date = 1993-09-29 | first = Edward N. | last = Rappaport | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | series = Tropical Depression Fourteen-E, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | archivedate = 2012-04-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120406084717/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1993/td14e/prenhc/prelim01.gif | format = GIF}}</ref><ref name="rainfallMX">{{cite book | first = David M. | last = Roth | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Data | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcrainfall.html | location = Camp Springs, Maryland | page = [http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/gert1993.html Hurricane Gert/T.D. #14E - September 14–28, 1993] | date = 2010-05-10 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131106050047/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcrainfall.html | archivedate = 2013-11-06}}</ref>。

== 防灾措施 ==
确认热带低气压发展形成后，[[哥斯达黎加|哥斯达黎加]]有关部门于9月14日向该国沿海地区发展了绿色警报{{#tag:ref|[[拉丁美洲|拉丁美洲]]飓风飓风警报采用蓝、绿、黄、橙和红来代表威胁程度，蓝色表示威胁最小，红色最大。<ref>{{cite web|archivedate=2012-07-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120710123008/http://geografica.cenapred.unam.mx/DocumentosSIAT/SIAT_CT.pdf |deadurl=yes |url=http://geografica.cenapred.unam.mx/DocumentosSIAT/SIAT_CT.pdf |title=Sistema de Alerta Temprana para Ciclones Tropicales |publisher=Secretaría de Gobernación |page=21 |accessdate=2014-07-19 |format=PDF |location=Mexico City, Mexico }}</ref>|group="注"}}<ref name="operations">{{cite book | archivedate = 2012-04-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120402234613/http://www.cne.go.cr/CEDO-CRID/pdf/spa/doc53/doc53-3a.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.cne.go.cr/CEDO-CRID/pdf/spa/doc53/doc53-3a.pdf | chapter = Part A: Informe de operaciónes Tormenta Gert | title = Plan regulador para la reconstrucción de las zonas afectadas por la Tormenta Tropical Gert | date = 1993-09-18 | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | publisher = Comisión Nacional de Emergencias | format = PDF | at = section 3, part A, pp. 2, 3, 7, [9], [15] | location = San José, Costa Rica}}</ref>。次日，该国大西洋沿海收到了[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]<ref name="warnings">{{cite report | location = Miami, Florida | series = Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | at = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/prenhc/prelim07.gif Table 3: Watch and warning summary, Hurricane Gert] | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Gert: 14-21 September 1993 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | first = Richard J. | last = Pasch | date = 1993-11-19 | accessdate = 2014-07-19}}</ref>。国家电视台和广播电台向公众发布警告信息，许多救援人员进入待命状态，确保在需要时及时介入。这使得多所医院以及高风险区域的居民得以及时有效地疏散<ref name="operations" />。9月15日，尼加拉瓜的大西洋沿海地区也收到了热带风暴警告，警告生效范围还从[[卡贝萨斯港|卡贝萨斯港]]向南延伸到邻近[[岛屿|岛屿]]<ref name="warnings" />。[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]提前发布的风暴警告让成百上千的居民得以在飓风来袭前及时撤离<ref name="honduras">{{cite report | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/honduras/honduras-floods-sep-1993-un-dha-situation-reports-1-4 | title = Honduras Floods Sep 1993 UN DHA Situation Reports 1 - 4 | author = United Nations Department of Humanitarian Affairs | date = 1993-09 | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | location = Geneva, Switzerland | archivedate = 2014-04-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140413234354/http://reliefweb.int/report/honduras/honduras-floods-sep-1993-un-dha-situation-reports-1-4 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。风暴出现袭击尤卡坦半岛的显著迹象时，从[[伯利兹|伯利兹]]向北至[[科苏梅尔岛|科苏梅尔岛]]之间的沿海地区从9月17日起处于热带风暴警告生效状态，直至次日飓风登陆时止<ref name="besttrack" /><ref name="warnings" />。

气旋仍处尤卡坦半岛上空时，墨西哥政府向[[韦拉克鲁斯_(韦拉克鲁斯州)|韦拉克鲁斯]]向北至[[塔毛利帕斯州|塔毛利帕斯州]]索托拉马里纳（{{lang|es|Soto la Marina}}）之间的墨西哥湾沿岸地区发布了[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]。到9月18日时，预警已升级成热带风暴警告并向南延伸至[[米纳蒂特兰_(韦拉克鲁斯州)|米纳蒂特兰]]，不过之前的预警区域在格特表现出增强趋势后升级成了[[热带气旋警告|飓风警告]]<ref name="besttrack" /><ref name="warnings" />。风暴来袭前，该国墨西哥湾沿岸多个港口中止了营运，生活在风险区域的人们也予撤离<ref>{{cite book | last1 = Gutiérrez | first1 = Prisciliano H. | last2 = Jiménez | first2 = Elias M. | last3 = de la Fuente | first3 = Rigoberto M. | last4 = Mendiola | first4 = Rubén Dario S. | location = Mexico City, Mexico | title = Las inundaciones causadas por el huracán "Gert" sus efectos en Hidalgo, San Luis Potosi, Tamaulipas y Veracruz | date = 1993-12 | publisher = El Sistema Nacional de Proteccion Civil, Secretaria de Gobernation; archived by CENAPRED | archivedate = 2012-04-25 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120425051859/http://www.crid.or.cr/digitalizacion/pdf/spa/doc15060/doc15060-1.pdf | url = http://www.crid.or.cr/digitalizacion/pdf/spa/doc15060/doc15060-1.pdf | page = 12 | format = [[PDF|PDF]]}}</ref>。飓风上岸后，所有的警告和预警均予中止<ref name="warnings" />。

