=== 哥斯达黎加 ===
虽然飓风格特的中心一直位于海上，但其大规模环流还是给哥斯达黎加全国各地带去了狂风暴雨，当地一所气象站在风暴经过期间一共记录下了332毫米降雨量<ref>{{cite conference | last1 = Fallas | last2 = Valverde | first1 = Jorge | url = http://www.una.ac.cr/redibec-cisda/ponencias/Climaticos/Jorge.pdf | title = Aplicación de ENOS como indicador de cambios en la precipitación máxima diaria en la cuenca del río Pejibaye y su impacto en inundaciones | first2 = Carmen | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120407121540/http://www.una.ac.cr/redibec-cisda/ponencias/Climaticos/Jorge.pdf | publisher = Universidad Nacional | location = Heredia, Costa Rica | accessdate = 2012-04-07 | year = 2007 | page = [20] | format = PDF | conference = III Congreso Iberoamericano Sobre Desarrollo Y Ambiente 5–9 de noviembre 2007 | conferenceurl = http://www.una.ac.cr/redibec-cisda/ponencias2008.html | archivedate = 2012-04-07 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。从[[地质学|地质学]]上来说，受灾最严重地区沉积层的[[水力传导系数|渗透系数]]低，因此土壤的含水量很容易饱和<ref name="reconstruction">{{cite report | url = http://www.cne.go.cr/CEDO-CRID/pdf/spa/doc210/doc210-contenido.pdf | title = Plan regular para la reconstrucción de las zonas afectadas por la Tormenta Tropical Gert | date = 1993-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140716193700/http://www.cne.go.cr/CEDO-CRID/pdf/spa/doc210/doc210-contenido.pdf | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | publisher = Comisión Nacional de Emergencias | format = PDF | pages = 2-5 | location = San José, Costa Rica | archivedate = 2014-07-16 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。最初的降水令许多河流水位上涨，增大了洪灾的威胁。[[滕皮斯克河|滕皮斯克河]]一度达到溢流的边缘，迫使邻近地区居民大规模疏散，但该河最终有惊无险，水位逐渐回落。持续数小时的倾盆大雨令包括[[克波斯|克波斯]]（{{lang|en|Quepos}}）、[[奥萨半岛|奥萨半岛]]在内的多个太平洋沿岸地区出现大范围洪灾和局部[[山崩|山体滑坡]]，造成许多道路和桥梁严重受损<ref name="operations" />。洪水摧毁了约2平方公里的[[香蕉|香蕉]]作物，还对[[油椰子|油椰子]]种植园构成中等程度破坏。小范围种植的[[芦苇_(植物)|芦苇]]、[[玉米|玉米]]、豆类和大米也受到严重影响。地方渔业因风暴受创，克波斯有许多小型船只受损严重<ref name="aftermath">{{cite book | url = http://cidbimena.desastres.hn/docum/crid/Riesgo/pdf/spa/doc53/doc53-2.pdf | format = PDF | at = section 2, p. [5] | chapter = Tormenta Tropical Gert Resumen Ejecutivo | title = Plan regulador para la reconstrucción de las zonas afectadas por la Tormenta Tropical Gert | year = 1993 | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140716144458/http://cidbimena.desastres.hn/docum/crid/Riesgo/pdf/spa/doc53/doc53-2.pdf | publisher = Comisión Nacional de Emergencias | location = San José, Costa Rica | archivedate = 2014-07-16 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[曼努埃尔安东尼奥国家公园|曼努埃尔安东尼奥国家公园]]因狂风变得满目疮痍，克波斯依靠[[旅游业|旅游业]]带动的[[经济|经济]]受到极大影响<ref name="reconstruction" />。

飓风还给该国造成了中等程度的财产损失，有27套民宅被毁，另外659套受损，其中大部分是因洪水导致。该国共计遭受了310万美元（1993年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|3100000|1993}}}}美元）的经济损失，其中超过170万美元（1993年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|1700000|1993}}}}美元）属[[基础设施|基础设施]]受损<ref>{{cite book | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120425051822/http://www.crid.or.cr/digitalizacion/pdf/spa/doc10533/doc10533-e1.pdf | url = http://www.crid.or.cr/digitalizacion/pdf/spa/doc10533/doc10533-e1.pdf | chapter = Informe final de operaciónes Tormenta Gert|title=Plan regulador para la reconstrucción de las zonas afectadas por la tormenta tropical Gert | date = 1993-09-25 | accessdate = 2011-10-07 | publisher = Comisión Nacional de Emergencias | format = PDF | at = section e, pp. 4, 13 | location = San José, Costa Rica | archivedate = 2012-04-25}}</ref>。约有1000人在风暴期间前往避难所躲避，由于准备及时，该国只有一人在飓风引起的山体滑坡掩埋了自己家时因心脏骤停死亡<ref name="operations" /><ref>{{cite news | url = http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1993-09-17/news/9309170011_1_tropical-storm-gert-costa-rica-nicaragua | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140413123113/http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1993-09-17/news/9309170011_1_tropical-storm-gert-costa-rica-nicaragua | title = Storm hits two nations | date = 1993-09-17 | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | work = Sun-Sentinel | location = Fort Lauderdale, Florida | archivedate = 2014-04-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

=== 尼加拉瓜 ===
风暴以热带风暴强度从尼加拉瓜登岸，该国一个月前刚刚经受热带风暴布雷特的摧残，土壤含水量已经饱和，格特带来的过量降雨可谓雪上加霜<ref name="dha">{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131017025214/http://reliefweb.int/report/nicaragua/nicaragua-tropical-storm-aug-1993-un-dha-situation-reports-1-8 | publisher = ReliefWeb | title = Nicaragua Tropical Storm Aug 1993 UN DHA Situation Reports 1 - 8 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/nicaragua/nicaragua-tropical-storm-aug-1993-un-dha-situation-reports-1-8 | date = 1993-09-17 | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | author = United Nations Department of Humanitarian Affairs | location = Geneva, Switzerland | archivedate = 2013-10-17}}</ref>。虽然气旋袭击的是大西洋海岸，但降雨量最大的却是该国北部和太平洋沿海地区。[[奇南德加省|奇南德加省]][[科林托_(尼加拉瓜)|科林托]]（{{lang|en|Corinto}}）的降雨量达到最高的452毫米，[[奇南德加|奇南德加]]和[[莱昂_(尼加拉瓜)|莱昂]]也分别达到447毫米和444毫米，[[首都|首都]][[马纳瓜|马纳瓜]]在风暴期间测得249毫米降水<ref>{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304045614/http://www.cepal.org/publicaciones/xml/7/15507/L372-1-EN.pdf | url = http://www.cepal.org/publicaciones/xml/7/15507/L372-1-EN.pdf | title = Nicaragua: Assessment of the damage caused by Hurricane Mitch, 1998: Implications for economic and social development and for the environment | date = 1999-04-19 | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | format = PDF | page = 12 | publisher = United Nations Economic Commission for Latin America and the Caribbean | location = Santiago, Chile | docket = LC/MEX/L.372}}</ref>。风暴从[[布卢菲尔兹|布卢菲尔兹]]附近登陆时产生的持续风速不超过每小时65公里<ref name="besttrack" />，但在近海产生的大浪有3.7米高。进入内陆后格特退化成热带低气压并继续在行经该国沿途产生中等[[烈风|烈风]]强度风力<ref name="miamiherald">{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-12-17 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/news/mh0916p1.gif | title = Weaker but blustery Gert inundates Nicaragua coast | first = John | last = Otis | work = The Miami Herald | date = 1993-09-16 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131217103539/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/news/mh0916p1.gif | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | location = Miami, Florida | series = [http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/ Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives]}}</ref>。

[[马伊斯群岛|大玉蜀黍岛]]近海有9艘渔船被狂风和大浪摧毁，两艘皮划艇及其上数量不明的乘客长眠大海。从布卢菲尔兹和（{{lang|en|Tasbapauni}}）附近登岸期间，格特引发了严重的沿海洪灾，促使近千居民和数百土著[[米斯基托人|米斯基托村民]]撤离<ref name="miamiherald" />。更为内陆的地区因长时间暴雨造成众多河流溢出，进一步引发灾难性的洪灾。拉马（{{lang|en|Rama}}）附近的一条河流上涨到超过正常水位10米，导致3900人无家可归，全镇约有80%被水淹没。[[里瓦斯省|里瓦斯省]]有多个社区因[[里瓦斯|里瓦斯]]附近一条河流泄洪而淹没，位于该国和哥斯达黎加边界的沿海社区卡德纳斯（{{lang|es|Cárdenas}}）暴雨持续了数天之久。整个[[博阿科省|博阿科省]]有5人因洪水丧生，约6000人受到影响<ref name="capra">{{cite book | publisher = Evaluación de Riesgos Naturales - América Latina - Consultores en Riesgos y Desastres | url = http://www.ecapra.org/capra_wiki/es_wiki/images/8/84/Eventos_Hist%C3%B3ricos_Importantes_NIC.pdf | format = PDF | pages = 42-43 | volume = Análisis probabilista de amenazas y riesgos naturales | series=  Revisión de eventos históricos importantes: Informe técnico ERN-CAPRA-T2-1 | title = Nicaragua | chapter = Estadísticas Específicas por Evento | accessdate = 2011-10-06 | archivedate = 2012-03-13 | location = Bogotá, Colombia | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120313043319/http://www.ecapra.org/capra_wiki/es_wiki/images/8/84/Eventos_Hist%C3%B3ricos_Importantes_NIC.pdf}} Hosted by ecapra.org.</ref>。山体滑坡还给许多桥梁和道路构成进一步破坏，当地交通受到严重扰乱<ref name="dha" />。全国14个省共有至少59套房屋被毁，约225套受到一定程度的破坏<ref name="dha" /><ref name="capra" />。风暴还导致该国的基础设施受损，并引起可观的经济损失<ref name="capra" />。有1万零448户家庭受到不同程度的影响，共11人遇难，27人失踪<ref name="capra" /><ref name="restof">{{cite journal | editors = Moisa, Ana Maria; Romano, Luis Ernesto; Velis, Louis Armano | title = [Various short articles] | format = PDF | archivedate = 2013-12-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131212195802/http://desastres.usac.edu.gt/documentos/pdf/spa/doc7784/doc7784-c.pdf | url = http://desastres.usac.edu.gt/documentos/pdf/spa/doc7784/doc7784-c.pdf | journal = Actualidades sobre desastres: Boletin de extensión cultural de CEPRODE: Centro de Protección para Desastres | publisher = Centro de Protección para Desastres | location = San Salvador, El Salvador | volume = 1 | issue = 1 | date = 1993 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | publisher = Biblioteca Virtual en Salud y Desastres | title = Actividades de las comunidades: la Coquera, los Coquitos, las Atarrayas. Concurso de Pintura Infantil 12 de Octubre 1993 | work = Memoria de actividades realizadas en conmemoración al Día Internacional para la Reducción de los Desastres Naturales - DIRDN : 8 al 15 de octubre 1993 | location = San Salvador, El Salvador | editor = Comité Técnico Interinstitucional de Desastres | archivedate = 2013-12-12 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131212195815/http://desastres.usac.edu.gt/documentos/pdf/spa/doc7784/doc7784.htm | url = http://desastres.usac.edu.gt/documentos/pdf/spa/doc7784/doc7784.htm | at = section 3 "Actividades de las comunidades", p. [8] | date = 1993-10-12 | accessdate = 2013-12-12 | format = PDF}}</ref>。该国一个月前刚刚遭受了热带风暴布雷特的摧残，因此无法精确统计出飓风格特造成损失的数字。两场风暴共计造成了约1070万美元（1993年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|10700000|1993}}}}美元）的破坏，其中大部分是私人财产损失<ref>{{cite conference|booktitle=Sistema Nacional de prevencion y manejo de desastres naturales |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131212195809/http://desastres.usac.edu.gt/documentos/pdf/spa/doc7149/doc7149-contenido.pdf |url=http://desastres.usac.edu.gt/documentos/pdf/spa/doc7149/doc7149-contenido.pdf |title=Impactos de los desastres naturales en Nicaragua |accessdate=2013-12-12 |first=José L. |last=Osorio |publisher=Biblioteca Virtual en Salud y Desastres |format=PDF |page=33 |year=1994 |location=Managua, Nicaragua |archivedate=2013-12-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

=== 洪都拉斯 ===
[[File:Surface_weather_map_Tropical_Depression_Gert_1993.gif|thumb]]，系统这时处于热带低气压强度。]]
虽然已减弱成热带低气压，但格特在穿越洪都拉斯的过程中继续产生大量降水，[[德古斯加巴|德古斯加巴]]记录下的降雨量有172毫米<ref name="prelim03">{{cite report | series = Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | page = 3 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140413140522/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/prenhc/prelim03.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/prenhc/prelim03.gif | title = Preliminary Report Hurricane Gert: 14-21 September 1993 | date = 1993-11-10 | first = Richard J. | last = Pasch | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2014-04-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[洪都拉斯行政区划|全国18个省]]中有13个受到毁灭性的洪水袭击，其中包括该国北部和莫斯基托斯海岸大部分地区，这些地区还在一个月前刚刚经受过热带风暴布雷特的袭击。风暴引发的洪灾影响了该区域约2.4万居民，并且几乎完全切断了周边地区的通讯<ref name="honduras" />。包括乌卢阿河在内的多条主要河流因降雨量太大导致溢出<ref name="red">{{cite book | url = http://www.desenredando.org/public/libros/1996/esyg/esyg_cap4-ESAPDH_dic-18-2002.pdf | format = PDF | title = Estado, sociedad y gestión de los desastres en América latina | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120425052126/http://www.desenredando.org/public/libros/1996/esyg/esyg_cap4-ESAPDH_dic-18-2002.pdf | first1 = Allan | last1 = Lavell | first2 = Eduardo | last2 = Franco | publisher = Red de Estudios Sociales en Prevención de Desastres en América Latina | pages = 19-20 | location = Panama City, Panama | archivedate = 2012-04-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，整个苏拉谷的多条河流情况尤为严重，该国第二大城市[[圣佩德罗苏拉|圣佩德罗苏拉]]及其位于[[科尔特斯省|科尔特斯省]]内的其他多个周边城市大部分区域被水淹没。上涨的水位促使许多居民撤离，[[拉蒙·比列达·莫拉莱斯国际机场|拉蒙·比列达·莫拉莱斯国际机场]]在洪灾期间中止了所有营运<ref name="honduras" />。

[[科尔特斯港|科尔特斯港]]因这场风暴变得满目疮痍，这里是中美洲最重要的港口城市之一<ref name="cortes">{{cite report | url = http://idbdocs.iadb.org/wsdocs/getdocument.aspx?docnum=1530074 | format = PDF | page = 3 | title = Puerto Cortés, Honduras: Después de la tempestad... vino la reforma | location = Washington, DC | publisher = Inter-American Development Bank | author = Iniciativa de Agua y Saneamiento | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | archivedate = 2012-04-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120425062637/http://idbdocs.iadb.org/wsdocs/getdocument.aspx?docnum=1530074 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[乔洛马|乔洛马]]有一条河流溢出，引发大面积洪灾<ref name="red" />，该地区仅因山体滑坡就导致6人遇难<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Cámara de Comercio e Industrias de Cortés | page = 2 | format = PDF | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.ccichonduras.org/pdf/CHOLOMA.pdf | title = Diagnostico ambiental de Choloma | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070128105051/http://www.ccichonduras.org/pdf/CHOLOMA.pdf | archivedate = 2007-01-28 | accessdate = 2017-01-28 | location = San Pedro Sula, Honduras}}</ref>。该国农业也遭受重创，包括香蕉、糖类和柑桔类在内的约23[[平方公里|平方公里]]位于低洼地区的种植园受到洪灾的严重破坏<ref name="honduras" /><ref>{{cite book | title = Country report: Nicaragua, Honduras | publisher = The Unit | author = Economist Intelligence Unit | year = 1994 | url = http://books.google.com/?id=pdeyAAAAIAAJ | page = 31 | location = London, United Kingdom}}</ref>。整个洪都拉斯的道路、桥梁和财产共在这场风暴中遭受了1000万美元（1993年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|10000000|1993}}}}美元）的损失<ref name="prelim03" />，有6万7447人直接受到影响，其中约有60%不得不离开家园。洪都拉斯政府在最后的公开声明中确认有27人死亡，另外还有12人失踪<ref name="honduras" />。

=== 中美洲其他地区 ===
途经中美洲期间，气旋令整个[[萨尔瓦多|萨尔瓦多]]的云层和降水都有所增多<ref name="elsalvador">{{cite book | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140413123803/http://www.desenredando.org/public/libros/1996/dtdei/DTDEI_todo_ene-7-2003.pdf | url = http://www.desenredando.org/public/libros/1996/dtdei/DTDEI_todo_ene-7-2003.pdf | title = De terremotos, derrumbes, e inundados | first1 = Mario | last1 = Lungo | first2 = Lina | last2 = Pohl | chapter = Las acciones de prevención y mitigación de desastres en El Salvador: Un sistema en construcción | publisher = Red de Estudios Sociales en Prevención de Desastres en América Latina | page = 34 | year = 2006 | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | format = PDF | location = Panama City, Panama | editor1-first = Mario | editor1-last = Lungo | editor2-first = Sonia | editor2-last = Baires | archivedate = 2014-04-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。强风将树木连根拔起或是令其树枝折断，对输电线缆构成破坏，造成多处[[停电|停电]]。倾盆大雨还在一条主要[[高速公路|高速公路]]沿线引发了破坏性的泥石流<ref name="restof" />。[[乌苏卢坦|乌苏卢坦]]（{{lang|en|Usulután}}）西南方向不远处的一条河流因水位上涨过快而不得不实行泄洪操作<ref name="elsalvador" />，导致附近种植园的约10平方公里农作物受到洪水的破坏。包括[[圣马科斯_(萨尔瓦多)|圣马科斯]]（{{lang|en|San Marcos}}）和[[圣维森特_(萨尔瓦多)|圣维森特]]（{{lang|en|San Vicente}}）在内的其他多个地区都报道因洪水而受到严重损失；[[聖米格爾_(薩爾瓦多)|圣米格尔]]也出现了一些财物和道路受损<ref name="restof" />。虽然风暴期间中止了捕捞作业，但还是有4名当地渔民在海上失踪<ref name="elsalvador" />。该国有近8000居民受到这一天气系统影响<ref name="restof" />，官方报告中称有12户民房被毁，5人丧生<ref name="elsalvador" />。

[[危地马拉|危地马拉]]有两万人受到气旋产生的倾盆大雨影响，还有一位女孩遇难。该国受到了相当可观的农业损失，但缺乏具体的报告和数据<ref name="restof" />。格特以热带风暴强度的最低标准从伯利兹市附近上岸，给沿海地区带去暴雨。位于近海岛屿上的一个气象站在风暴期间记录下了241毫米降雨量<ref>{{cite report | year = 1993 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | title = Hourly data from Hunting Caye | series = Hurricane Gert, Hurricane Wallet Digital Archives | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/preloc/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121022222118/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1993/gert/preloc/ | archivedate = 2012-10-22 | deadurl = no | location = Miami, Florida}}</ref>。不过雨量虽大，伯利兹市内却只出现了轻度洪灾<ref>{{cite book | title = WMO bulletin | volume = 44 | publisher = World Meteorological Organization | year = 2005 | page = 369 | url = http://books.google.com/books/about/WMO_bulletin.html?id=9IdVAAAAMAAJ | location = Geneva, Switzerland | accessdate = 2014-07-19}}</ref>。

